title: Laney & Lu
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Juice bar
description: A 100% vegan/vegetarian restaurant serving mostly vegan food. Clearly states when dairy products are used. Serves wraps, bowls, smoothies, juices, coffee, tea and more.  Serves breakfast until 11am. Gluten free options are available. Buys local whenever possible and most everything is certified organic.
